title: Queen + Paul Rodgers - Cosmos Rocks [320k MP3]
description:
The Cosmos Rocks is the debut studio album by Queen + Paul Rodgers released on 15 September 2008. It contains 14 new tracks written by Brian May, Paul Rodgers and Roger Taylor. This is the first studio album of new material from the two remaining members of Queen since 1995's Made in Heaven, and is the only studio collaboration to date with Paul Rodgers
